# VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_ESTIMATED_MAX_SPEED

## Summary
Get the estimated top speed of the vehicle (with mods) on a flat surface

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle: Index - vehicle of interest

## Returns
* **FLOAT**
